TI  - Two amino acid residues in the N-terminal region of the polymerase acidic protein determine the virulence of Eurasian avian-like H1N1 swine influenza viruses in mice
AU  - Yang, Yuying
AU  - Xu, Chengzhi
AU  - Zhang, Naixin
AU  - Wan, Yunfei
AU  - Wu, Yunpu
AU  - Meng, Fei
AU  - Chen, Yan
AU  - Yang, Huanliang
