TI  - Influenza A virus acquires enhanced pathogenicity and transmissibility after serial passages in swine
AU  - Wei, Kai
AU  - Sun, Honglei
AU  - Sun, Zhenhong
AU  - Sun, Yipeng
AU  - Kong, Weili
AU  - Pu, Juan
