TI  - Emergence of H5N1 avian influenza viruses with reduced sensitivity to neuraminidase inhibitors and novel reassortants in Lao People's Democratic Republic
AU  - Boltz, David A.
AU  - Douangngeun, Bounlom
AU  - Phommachanh, Phouvong
AU  - Sinthasak, Settha
