TI  - Rapid emergence of a virulent PB2 E627K variant during adaptation of highly pathogenic avian influenza H7N7 virus to mice
AU  - de Jong, Rineke M. C.
AU  - Stockhofe-Zurwieden, Norbert
AU  - Verheij, Eline S.
