TI  - Accumulation of human-adapting mutations during circulation of A(H1N1)pdm09 influenza virus in humans in the United Kingdom
AU  - Elderfield, Ruth A.
AU  - Watson, Simon J.
AU  - Godlee, Alexandra
AU  - Adamson, Walt E.
AU  - Thompson, Catherine I.
AU  - Dunning, Jake
