TI  - Analysis of the responsible site for favipiravir resistance in RNA-dependent RNA polymerase of influenza virus A/PR/8/34 (H1N1) using site-directed mutagenesis
AU  - Komeno, Takashi
AU  - Furuta, Yousuke
AU  - Nakajima, Nozomi
AU  - Tani, Hideki
