TI  - In Vitro and In Vivo Characterization of Novel Neuraminidase Substitutions in Influenza A(H1N1)pdm09 Virus Identified Using Laninamivir-Mediated In Vitro Selection
AU  - Lloren, Khristine Kaith S.
AU  - Kwon, Jin Jung
AU  - Choi, Won-Suk
