TI  - An influenza A(H5N8) virus isolated during an outbreak at a poultry farm in Russia in 2017 has an N294S substitution in the neuraminidase and shows reduced susceptibility to oseltamivir
AU  - Svyatchenko, Svetlana V.
AU  - Goncharova, Natalia I.
