TI  - Screening for Neuraminidase Inhibitor Resistance Markers among Avian Influenza Viruses of the N4, N5, N6, and N8 Neuraminidase Subtypes
AU  - Choi, Won-Suk
AU  - Jeong, Ju Hwan
AU  - Kwon, Jin Jung
AU  - Ahn, Su Jeong
AU  - Lloren, Khristine Kaith S.
AU  - Kwon, Hyeok-Il
